		</specificfeedback>
    <questionnote>
				<text>\( z_1= {@z1@} \) and \( z_2 = {@z2@}\) so \(\qquad z = z_1^2 z_2 =  {@ta1_c@}, \; \; |z| = {@ta2@}, \; \; \text{arg}(z) =  {@ta3@} \).</text>
		</questionnote>
